## Project Setup

### 1. Clone the Project

```bash
http://102.223.8.140:9000/{{package_name}}/{{package_name}}_backend.git
cd {{package_name}}_backend
````

### 2. Create & Activate Virtual Environment

```bash
python3 -m venv venv
source venv/bin/activate
```

### 3. Install Dependencies

```bash
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

